title: It's Like, You Know... (1999-2000) - Complete TV Series
description:
It's Like, You Know... is an American sitcom broadcast by ABC from 1999-2000 created by Peter Mehlman (writer & producer on Seinfeld). 

It stars Jennifer Grey (Dirty Dancing) playing herself, Evan Handler (Californication), Steven Eckholdt (L.A. Law), A. J. Langer (My So-Called Life) and Chris Eigeman (Malcolm in the Middle). 

The series is about life in Los Angeles viewed through the eyes of a diehard New Yorker. The writer Arthur Garment moves to L.A. to write a book about how much he loathes this city with its vapid and superficial culture. Although the longer he stays, the more he's getting used to it.

Here you have the complete series including all originally unaired episodes in good quality. Enjoy!
